OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782061560
OL,3,CKing to make history and publish his
OL,4,Cpersonal tax bill
OL,6,FThe King is to become the first head
OL,7,Fof state to reveal their personal tax
OL,8,Fbill to help enhance transparency
OL,9,Faround royal finances.
OL,11,FCharles will publish his financial
OL,12,Fdetails as his royal household seeks
OL,13,Fto increase "clarity and
OL,14,Faccessibility" around the monarchy's
OL,15,Ffinances by producing a new report on
OL,16,Fthe subject.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782061560
OL,3,CKing to make history and publish his
OL,4,Cpersonal tax bill
OL,6,FThe decision by the King, who has
OL,7,Fspent the week at Royal Ascot, is in
OL,8,Fcontrast to the Prince of Wales who
OL,9,Fhas not disclosed the tax he has paid
OL,10,Fsince becoming heir to the throne.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782061560
OL,3,CKing to make history and publish his
OL,4,Cpersonal tax bill
OL,6,FA Buckingham Palace spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"While this is the first time a
OL,8,Fmonarch has shared this personal tax
OL,9,Finformation, you may recall it was
OL,10,Fsimilarly released by His Majesty when
OL,11,Fhe was prince of Wales.
OL,13,F"The decision to do so as Sovereign
OL,14,Fhas come at the express wish of the
OL,15,FKing himself, as part of the
OL,16,Fadaptations carried across since
OL,17,Faccession."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782061560
OL,3,CKing to make history and publish his
OL,4,Cpersonal tax bill
OL,6,FThe King's private sources of income
OL,7,Fcould include money from investments
OL,8,For trading profits, funds generated by
OL,9,Fhis private estates of Balmoral and
OL,10,FSandringham and private savings.
OL,12,FThe Duchy of Lancaster estate, a
OL,13,Fprivate portfolio of land, investments
OL,14,Fand office, retail and industrial
OL,15,Fproperties, also provide the King with
OL,16,Fan annual income which in In 2024/
OL,17,F2025, stood at #26.8 million.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782061560
OL,3,CKing to make history and publish his
OL,4,Cpersonal tax bill
OL,6,FIt was designed to give the monarch of
OL,7,Fthe day an independent source of
OL,8,Fincome, historically known as the
OL,9,FPrivy Purse, used for both official
OL,10,Fand private expenditure and for
OL,11,Fmeeting the expenses of other members
OL,12,Fof the royal family.
OL,14,FCharles voluntary pays income tax on
OL,15,Fall his private income, and capital
OL,16,Fgains tax on relevant elements of his
OL,17,Fassets, as laid out in the Memorandum
OL,18,Fof Understanding on Royal Taxation
OL,19,F2023, agreed by Government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782061560
OL,3,CKing to make history and publish his
OL,4,Cpersonal tax bill
OL,6,FLater this week the King's total
OL,7,Fpersonal tax information for the 2024-
OL,8,F25 financial year will be published,
OL,9,Falongside other reports on royal
OL,10,Ffinances.
OL,12,FHis 2025-26 tax details will be
OL,13,Freleased next year when their audit
OL,14,Fhas been completed.
OL,16,FWilliam receives an income from the
OL,17,FDuchy of Cornwall, a billion-pound
OL,18,Fhereditary estate featuring The Oval
OL,19,Fcricket ground and Dartmoor Prison,
OL,20,Fproviding the heir to the throne with
OL,21,Ffunds independent of the monarch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782061560
OL,3,CKing to make history and publish his
OL,4,Cpersonal tax bill
OL,6,FThe prince received nearly #23 million
OL,7,Flast financial year from the duchy and
OL,8,Fvoluntarily pays the highest rate of
OL,9,Fincome tax, once official costs have
OL,10,Fbeen deducted, but the amount he pays
OL,11,Fin tax is not disclosed.
OL,13,FIt was reported recently he is to
OL,14,Finvest #500 million from selling off a
OL,15,Ffifth of his duchy estate and other
OL,16,Ftransactions to have a "positive
OL,17,Fimpact on the world".
OL,26,@xD@XOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
