OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782061560
OL,3,CKing to make history and publish his
OL,4,Cpersonal tax bill
OL,6,FAccounts detailing the Sovereign
OL,7,FGrant, which funds the official duties
OL,8,Fof the royal family, will be published
OL,9,Fat a press briefing this week
OL,10,Falongside a separate extensive new
OL,11,Froyal household report on royal
OL,12,Ffinances.
OL,14,FFigures from last year showed the
OL,15,FSovereign Grant stood at #86.3
OL,16,Fmillion, comprising #51.8 million for
OL,17,Fcore elements like travel and payroll
OL,18,Fcosts and #34.5 million to fund the
OL,19,FBuckingham Palace Reservicing
OL,20,FProgramme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782061560
OL,3,CKing to make history and publish his
OL,4,Cpersonal tax bill
OL,6,FSpeaking about the new report a
OL,7,FBuckingham Palace spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Our aim is to explain all elements of
OL,9,Froyal finances in a way that further
OL,10,Fenhances clarity and accessibility,
OL,11,Fwhile also placing it in its
OL,12,Fhistorical and constitutional context."
OL,14,FAlongside the new publication and the
OL,15,FSovereign Grant report, the Duchy of
OL,16,FLancaster's accounts will also be
OL,17,Fpublished at another press briefing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
