OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782061560
OL,3,CKing to make history and publish his
OL,4,Cpersonal tax bill
OL,6,FA Buckingham Palace spokesperson said
OL,7,Fabout the changes: "In order
OL,8,Fconstantly to improve, and to
OL,9,Fencourage wider understanding of our
OL,10,Faccountability, the royal household
OL,11,Fhas been considering options to
OL,12,Fenhance this transparency still
OL,13,Ffurther ` and can today announce
OL,14,Fadditional measures in keeping with
OL,15,Four public service priorities.
OL,17,F"To put it simply: we continue to
OL,18,Fmodernise and evolve."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
